(4, 1, '172211852807956', '172211852807956_1841107759251682', 'Unbelievably BAD', 'Tex and SHACKLΣS talk two-timing drummers and getting crustier with age.', 'link', 'Our latest interview with UB! \n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/unbelievablybad/posts/1623090411076344', 'SHACKLΣS shared Unbelievably BAD''s post.', '', '[]', '', '[{"id":"172211852807956","name":"SHACKL\\u03a3S","type":"page","offset":0,"length":8},{"id":"961339017251490","name":"Unbelievably BAD","type":"page","offset":16,"length":16}]', 'shared_story', 'https://unbelievablybadmag.com/2017/07/13/shackles-on-lifeless-paradise-10-and-doubling-their-drumming-fun/', '', '', '', '', '', '2017-07-12T23:32:42+0000', '2017-07-12T23:32:42+0000', 1499902362, '', '{"data":[],"summary":{"order":"chronological","total_count":0,"can_comment":false}}', '', '{"data":[{"description":"Byron-born hardcore band been spending most their lives livin\\u2019 in a Lifeless Paradise. That\\u2019ll make anyone cranky.","media":{"image":{"height":623,"src":"https:\\/\\/scontent.xx.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t39.2147-6\\/c137.0.623.623\\/p624x624\\/19666854_1623085611076824_7172122916442603520_n.jpg?oh=2bda61e3a77392a2255030f43b93f26b&oe=5A319EAF","width":623}},"target":{"url":"https:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Funbelievablybadmag.com%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2Fshackles-on-lifeless-paradise-10-and-doubling-their-drumming-fun%2F&h=ATNVR1ZujTf4JoAIn-lbSZk9_XFL44xGnpuk-04gRejtGfrozeodpbrRDlijyYQ26y9tH0-GxNf8SwHjCV9-Rm_Pb9nkz1oUM-c&s=1&enc=AZNoTaZ9O2s47a-2i8p3qCPVTBZO5VX-Sw4cVaRY4pt3n-sLclowwaln6pgREzsZR9XZU8hIFdo-AeAplgDUdIFY"},"title":"Shackles on Lifeless Paradise 10\\u2033 and doubling their drumming fun","type":"share","url":"https:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Funbelievablybadmag.com%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2Fshackles-on-lifeless-paradise-10-and-doubling-their-drumming-fun%2F&h=ATNVR1ZujTf4JoAIn-lbSZk9_XFL44xGnpuk-04gRejtGfrozeodpbrRDlijyYQ26y9tH0-GxNf8SwHjCV9-Rm_Pb9nkz1oUM-c&s=1&enc=AZNoTaZ9O2s47a-2i8p3qCPVTBZO5VX-Sw4cVaRY4pt